<i>You were there. then you were gone</i>

547
00:32:50.551 --> 00:32:53.972
<i>Now I'm tracin' all my steps to you</i>
<i>And oh my God</i>

548
00:32:54.055 --> 00:32:58.476
<i>Oh. I think I'm losin' my mind</i>

549
00:32:58.559 --> 00:33:02.480
<i>Over here. over you. every night</i>

550
00:33:02.563 --> 00:33:07.485
<i>Both hands holding on to the wire</i>
<i>Impossible</i>

551
00:33:07.568 --> 00:33:09.487
<i>Fight over here</i>

552
